### How It Works

1. **Page View Tracking:** Automatically tracks all page transitions via React Router
2. **Data Collection:** Collects visitor metrics, page views, and user interactions
3. **Vercel Integration:** Once deployed, reports data to `/_vercel/insights/view`
4. **Dashboard:** Analytics data visible in Vercel Project Dashboard > Analytics tab
5. **Route Support:** React Router v6 routes are automatically tracked

