### Deployment Checklist

Before deploying to Vercel, ensure:

- [ ] Repository pushed to GitHub/GitLab
- [ ] Repository connected to Vercel project
- [ ] Environment variables configured (if needed)
- [ ] Web Analytics enabled in Vercel Dashboard:
  - Go to Project Settings > Analytics tab
  - Click "Enable" button
  - Confirm routes scoped at `/_vercel/insights/*` are created

### Post-Deployment Steps

1. **Initial Setup (One-time):**
   - Deploy application: `vercel deploy` or via Git push
   - Enable Web Analytics in Vercel Dashboard
   - System automatically adds `/_vercel/insights/*` routes

2. **Data Collection:**
   - Analytics begins tracking on next deployment
   - Initial data appears within 24 hours
   - Full analytics dashboard available after 1-2 weeks

3. **Monitor Analytics:**
   - Open Vercel Dashboard
   - Navigate to Project > Analytics tab
   - View page views, visitor metrics, and performance data

### Optional Enhancements

The following can be added for enhanced tracking:

```javascript
